00:04:31.188 --> 00:04:35.224
Rekel je: "Pa ne zaradi mene,
meni ste všeč."

00:04:35.224 --> 00:04:36.526
(Smeh)

00:04:36.526 --> 00:04:40.257
In to sem naredil tudi jaz.
Zasmejal sem se.

00:04:40.257 --> 00:04:42.233
Rekel je: "Ampak tu je problem:

00:04:42.233 --> 00:04:46.542
Če tebe spustim noter,
se bodo ostali izselili

00:04:46.542 --> 00:04:49.725
in tega si ne morem privoščiti."

00:04:49.725 --> 00:04:52.052
Dejal je: "Enostavno ti ne morem
dati prostora."

00:04:52.052 --> 00:04:54.603
Čeprav to ni bilo spodbudno,
me ni ustavilo.

00:04:54.603 --> 00:04:55.933
Še naprej sem iskal

00:04:55.933 --> 00:05:00.233
in pogledal sem na konec mesta
v Mountain Home-u,